{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843421800,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d7883511d001jI6NA7kBar53uN","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/plan.md","content":"# AR-004 Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Project Structure Setup\n\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/` directory structure\n- [ ] Create subpackages: `server/`, `handlers/`, `middleware/`, `config/`\n- [ ] Define interface contracts between layers\n\n## Phase 2: HTTP Server Foundation\n\n- [ ] Implement base server structure with configurable options\n- [ ] Setup HTTP router (choose framework: Gin/Chi/std lib)\n- [ ] Implement server lifecycle (start, stop, graceful shutdown)\n- [ ] Add health check endpoint\n\n## Phase 3: Middleware Implementation\n\n- [ ] Request logging middleware\n- [ ] Error recovery/panic handling middleware\n- [ ] Request ID generation middleware\n- [ ] CORS middleware (if needed)\n- [ ] Request timeout middleware\n\n## Phase 4: API Endpoints & Handlers\n\n- [ ] Define RESTful routes for workload operations:\n  - POST /api/v1/workloads - Create workload\n  - GET /api/v1/workloads - List workloads\n  - GET /api/v1/workloads/:id - Get workload details\n  - PUT /api/v1/workloads/:id - Update workload\n  - DELETE /api/v1/workloads/:id - Delete workload\n- [ ] Implement handler stubs (business logic to be filled in later AR)\n\n## Phase 5: Response & Error Handling\n\n- [ ] Define standardized JSON response structure\n- [ ] Implement error response formatter\n- [ ] Map internal errors to HTTP status codes\n- [ ] Add validation error handling\n\n## Phase 6: Configuration\n\n- [ ] Define server configuration schema\n- [ ] Implement configuration loading from file/env\n- [ ] Support for port, timeout, and middleware settings\n\n## Phase 7: Testing & Validation\n\n- [ ] Unit tests for middleware\n- [ ] Unit tests for handlers\n- [ ] Integration tests for server startup\n- [ ] Verify graceful shutdown behavior\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [ ] Code follows Go best practices\n- [ ] All exported functions have documentation\n- [ ] Error handling is consistent\n- [ ] Configuration is externalized\n- [ ] Tests cover happy path and error cases\n- [ ] No business logic in framework layer\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/plan.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/plan.md","time":{"start":1775843421775,"end":1775843421799}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843421802,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d7883836a001nzazFYVkWmQGd0","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","content":"# AR-004 Design Document\n\n## Overview\n\nThis document describes the HTTP service framework design for WorkloadManager.\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                        HTTP Server                           │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐  │\n│  │   Router    │──│ Middleware  │──│      Handlers       │  │\n│  │             │  │   Chain     │  │                     │  │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n                    ┌─────────────────────┐\n                    │  Business Logic     │\n                    │  (Future AR)        │\n                    └─────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Component Design\n\n### 1. Server (`pkg/workloadmanager/server/`)\n\nResponsible for HTTP server lifecycle management.\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Server initialization with configuration\n- Route registration\n- Middleware setup\n- Graceful shutdown handling\n\n### 2. Router (`pkg/workloadmanager/server/router.go`)\n\nDefines API routes and maps them to handlers.\n\n**Routes:**\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| GET | /health | Health check endpoint |\n| POST | /api/v1/workloads | Create workload |\n| GET | /api/v1/workloads | List workloads |\n| GET | /api/v1/workloads/:id | Get workload |\n| PUT | /api/v1/workloads/:id | Update workload |\n| DELETE | /api/v1/workloads/:id | Delete workload |\n\n### 3. Middleware (`pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/`)\n\nProvides cross-cutting concerns.\n\n**Planned Middleware:**\n- `Logger`: Request/response logging\n- `Recovery`: Panic recovery\n- `RequestID`: Unique request ID generation\n- `Timeout`: Request timeout enforcement\n\n### 4. Handlers (`pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`)\n\nHTTP request handlers (stubs for now).\n\n### 5. Config (`pkg/workloadmanager/config/`)\n\nConfiguration management.\n\n## Response Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"error\": null,\n  \"request_id\": \"uuid\"\n}\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n| Error Type | HTTP Status | Description |\n|------------|-------------|-------------|\n| ValidationError | 400 | Invalid request parameters |\n| NotFoundError | 404 | Resource not found |\n| InternalError | 500 | Server internal error |\n\n## Decisions\n\n*To be filled during implementation*\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. Which HTTP framework to use? (Gin, Chi, or std lib)\n2. TLS support requirements?\n3. Rate limiting strategy?\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775843421779,"end":1775843421801}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843421804,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d7883c496001a9ggJgXy5F70CO","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","content":"# AR-004 Task Breakdown\n\n## T1: Project Structure\n- [ ] Create directory layout\n- [ ] Define package interfaces\n- [ ] Setup go.mod dependencies\n\n## T2: Server Implementation\n- [ ] Server struct definition\n- [ ] Configuration options\n- [ ] Start/Stop methods\n- [ ] Graceful shutdown\n\n## T3: Router Setup\n- [ ] Route definitions\n- [ ] Handler registration\n- [ ] Route groups\n\n## T4: Middleware Chain\n- [ ] Logging middleware\n- [ ] Recovery middleware\n- [ ] RequestID middleware\n- [ ] Timeout middleware\n\n## T5: Handler Stubs\n- [ ] CreateWorkload handler\n- [ ] ListWorkloads handler\n- [ ] GetWorkload handler\n- [ ] UpdateWorkload handler\n- [ ] DeleteWorkload handler\n- [ ] Health handler\n\n## T6: Response & Error\n- [ ] Response struct definition\n- [ ] Error types\n- [ ] Error mapper\n- [ ] JSON writer utility\n\n## T7: Configuration\n- [ ] Config struct\n- [ ] Config loader\n- [ ] Default values\n- [ ] Environment variable support\n\n## T8: Testing\n- [ ] Server tests\n- [ ] Middleware tests\n- [ ] Handler tests\n- [ ] Integration tests\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775843421782,"end":1775843421803}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843421805,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d7883e2f7001u00T0dUr6YyElw","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tests.md","content":"# AR-004 Test Specifications\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Server Tests\n- `TestNewServer`: Verify server creation with options\n- `TestServerStart`: Verify server starts and listens\n- `TestServerStop`: Verify graceful shutdown\n- `TestServerWithConfig`: Verify configuration applied\n\n### Middleware Tests\n- `TestLoggingMiddleware`: Verify request logging\n- `TestRecoveryMiddleware`: Verify panic recovery\n- `TestRequestIDMiddleware`: Verify ID generation\n- `TestTimeoutMiddleware`: Verify request timeout\n\n### Handler Tests\n- `TestHealthHandler`: Verify health endpoint\n- `TestCreateWorkloadHandler`: Verify create endpoint stub\n- `TestListWorkloadsHandler`: Verify list endpoint stub\n- `TestGetWorkloadHandler`: Verify get endpoint stub\n- `TestUpdateWorkloadHandler`: Verify update endpoint stub\n- `TestDeleteWorkloadHandler`: Verify delete endpoint stub\n\n### Response Tests\n- `TestJSONResponse`: Verify response format\n- `TestErrorResponse`: Verify error response format\n- `TestStatusCodeMapping`: Verify error to status mapping\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Server Integration\n- `TestServerStartup`: Full server startup test\n- `TestRoutesRegistered`: Verify all routes exist\n- `TestMiddlewareChain`: Verify middleware executes\n\n### API Endpoints\n- `TestHealthEndpoint`: GET /health returns 200\n- `TestCreateWorkloadEndpoint`: POST /api/v1/workloads\n- `TestListWorkloadsEndpoint`: GET /api/v1/workloads\n- `TestGetWorkloadEndpoint`: GET /api/v1/workloads/:id\n- `TestUpdateWorkloadEndpoint`: PUT /api/v1/workloads/:id\n- `TestDeleteWorkloadEndpoint`: DELETE /api/v1/workloads/:id\n\n## Test Data\n\n### Mock Workload Objects\n```go\n// Sample workload for testing\nmockWorkload := Workload{\n    ID:   \"test-workload-001\",\n    Name: \"test-workload\",\n    // ... other fields\n}\n```\n\n### Test Scenarios\n\n| Scenario | Input | Expected Output |\n|----------|-------|-----------------|\n| Health check | GET /health | 200 OK, status: healthy |\n| Create workload | Valid JSON payload | 201 Created |\n| Create workload | Invalid JSON | 400 Bad Request |\n| Get workload | Valid ID | 200 OK, workload data |\n| Get workload | Invalid ID | 404 Not Found |\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tests.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/tests.md","time":{"start":1775843421785,"end":1775843421804}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843421807,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d7884177a00147DWZ0fXi4zwT9","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md","content":"# AR-004 Notes\n\n## Research Notes\n\n*To be filled during implementation*\n\n### Framework Comparison\n\n| Framework | Pros | Cons |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| Gin | Fast, popular, middleware support | External dependency |\n| Chi | Lightweight, std lib compatible | Less features than Gin |\n| std lib | No deps, standard | More boilerplate |\n\n### References\n\n- [Go HTTP Server Patterns](https://go.dev/doc/articles/wiki/)\n- [Graceful Shutdown](https://go.dev/blog/graceful-server-shutdown)\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n*To be filled during development*\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n*To be recorded during implementation*\n\n## Blockers/Issues\n\n*To be tracked*\n\n## Follow-up Items\n\n*To be added as discovered*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md","time":{"start":1775843421788,"end":1775843421806}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843422173,"sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","part":{"id":"prt_d788324d8001RwkMdAt208RgWX","messageID":"msg_d788317ba001kdGGxaTZWj7b4A","sessionID":"ses_2877d5538ffeSqhj0OWpDOwK7k","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-004\ntitle: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\nmodule: pkg/workloadmanager\nlanguage: Go\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\n# Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n# Language: Go\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: service-framework\n  description: |\n    Build the HTTP service framework for WorkloadManager, providing RESTful APIs\n    for workload lifecycle management including create, query, update, and delete\n    operations. The framework should support middleware, routing, error handling,\n    and standardized response formats.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - pkg/workloadmanager/server package structure\n    - HTTP router and handler setup\n    - RESTful API endpoints for workload management\n    - Middleware (logging, error recovery, request validation)\n    - Response formatting and error handling\n    - Configuration loading for server settings\n  out:\n    - Business logic implementation (separate AR)\n    - Authentication/Authorization (separate AR)\n    - Database persistence layer (separate AR)\n    - Metrics and monitoring (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - HTTP server starts and listens on configured port\n  - Router correctly routes requests to handlers\n  - Middleware chain executes for all requests\n  - Standardized JSON response format\n  - Proper error handling with HTTP status codes\n  - Graceful shutdown support\n  - Configuration-driven server settings\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n  - https://github.com/gin-gonic/gin (or chosen framework)\n  - AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime types\n  - AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter types\n  - AR-003: CRD Shared Types\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775843421769,"end":1775843422170}}}}
